RJR Nabisco Inc filed with theSecurities and Exchange Commission for a shelf offering of upto 500 mln dlrs of debt securities on terms to be set at thetime of sale.    The company said proceeds will be used for generalcorporate purposes including repurchases of RJR securities.    Proceeds also may be used for working capital, reduction ofshort-term debt and capital expenditures, it said.    Underwriters for the offering were not named in the draftprospectus. Reuter&#3;